lyrics:
[Verse 1]
In the darkness, their eyes shine bright
Four-legged warriors, prowling in the night
Claws like razors, they strike with might
Fearless feline forces, ready to ignite

[Chorus]
Cats of steel, they will never yield
Roaring hearts, their power concealed
Unleashed fury, they're breaking the seal
In this New Wave of British Heavy Metal, they are revealed
style: New wave of british heavy metal
